highlights.text: Selena Gomez has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Rare” is the highest at #12.
“TOES (feat. Lil Baby & Moneybagg Yo)” by DaBaby, Lil Baby, and Moneybagg Yo is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 64 spots at #71.
“Life Is Good (feat. Drake)” by Future and Drake is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #3.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 158 weeks straight.
